import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './app'
import { BrowserRouter} from "react-router-dom"
import Inputform from './inputform'

const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));
root.render(
  <React.StrictMode>
    <App />
    <Inputform />
  </React.StrictMode>
);
